headline.print_headline: Estonia, Sweden Honor 1994 Ferry Disaster Victims
headline.main: Estonia, Sweden Honor 1994 Ferry Disaster Victims

lead_paragraph: Hundreds of people gathered Sunday in Estonia and Sweden to commemorate 852 people killed in one of Europe's worst peacetime disasters 20 years ago when the Estonia ferry sank en route from Tallinn to Stockholm.
